javac.tree.JCTree.Visitor

  • 使用JCTree.Visitor的程序包 
    程序包 说明
    javac.comp  
    javac.jvm  
    javac.tree  

    • javac.comp中JCTree.Visitor的使用

      javac.comp中JCTree.Visitor的子类 
      限定符和类型 类和说明
      class  Attr
      This is the main context-dependent analysis phase in GJC.
      class  DeferredAttr
      This is an helper class that is used to perform deferred type-analysis.
      class  Enter
      This class enters symbols for all encountered definitions into the symbol table.
      class  Flow.AssignAnalyzer
      This pass implements (i) definite assignment analysis, which ensures that each variable is assigned when used and (ii) definite unassignment analysis, which ensures that no final variable is assigned more than once.
      class  LambdaToMethod
      This pass desugars lambda expressions into static methods This is NOT part of any supported API.
      class  Lower
      This pass translates away some syntactic sugar: inner classes, class literals, assertions, foreach loops, etc.
      class  MemberEnter
      This is the second phase of Enter, in which classes are completed by entering their members into the class scope using MemberEnter.complete().
      class  TransTypes
      This pass translates Generic Java to conventional Java.

    • javac.jvm中JCTree.Visitor的使用

      javac.jvm中JCTree.Visitor的子类 
      限定符和类型 类和说明
      class  Gen
      This pass maps flat Java (i.e. without inner classes) to bytecodes.

      限定符和类型 类和说明
      class  Pretty
      Prints out a tree as an indented Java source program.
      class  TreeScanner
      A subclass of Tree.Visitor, this class defines a general tree scanner pattern.
      class  TreeTranslator
      A subclass of Tree.Visitor, this class defines a general tree translator pattern.
